title: Novo Nordisk pops 8% after Hims & Hers pulls copycat Wegovy weight-loss pill
summary_full: Novo Nordisk shares jumped 8% Monday after Hims & Hers said it will pull its copycat weight-loss pill off the market.
summary_public: Novo Nordisk shares jumped 8% Monday after Hims & Hers said it will pull its copycat weight-loss pill off the market.
